module ietf-yang-types { namespace "urn:ietf:params:xml:ns:yang:ietf-yang-types"; prefix yang;
organization "IETF Network Modeling (NETMOD) Working Group"; contact "WG Web: <https://datatracker.ietf.org/wg/netmod/> WG List: <mailto:netmod@ietf.org>
Editor: Jürgen Schönwälder <mailto:jschoenwaelder@constructor.university>"; description "This module contains a collection of generally useful derived YANG data types.
